"noticeId\":14,\"noticeTitle\":\"河北地质大学老校区四季风光纪录片等视频拍摄制作项目询价公告\",\"noticeType\":\"2\",\"notice_courseId\":1,\"notice_user_type\":\" \",\"params\":{},\"status\":\"0\",\"updateBy\":\"admin\",\"updateTime\":\"2024-10-31 19:34:49\"}', '{\"msg\":\"操作成功\",\"code\":200}', 0, NULL, '2024-11-04 16:32:57', 13);
